##Deployment
1.Download sorces from github repository.
2.Create Database on your Database Server.
3.Make release build.
4.Copy \Build\Assembly\ folder to your web folder
5.Go to ~\Assembly\ folder, open setup.cmd and change connection string to proper one.
6.Go to ~\Assembly\Packages see Ach.Fulfillment.Web.deploy-readme.txt for further instractions




Job configuration
1. Go to jobs.xml file
2. Open "job-data-map" section - there in section "value" you should put path to the directory where 
genarated files will be stored.
3. Open "trigger" section - there you can configure when your job will be run. For more information
look at http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cron